UNDERLYING PROOF SYSTEM
is
HILBERT-STYLE AXIOMATIC PROOFS
of
SEQUENTS


A sequent has form:

{A°, A¬...} … C

where {A°, A¬...} and C are
formulae or schema expressions
.DE
