.KS
.DS

Hilbert-Style means:


(1)	forward proof

(2)	few rules

(3)	many axioms



Other objectives:

(i)	Minimal set of sufficient rules/axioms
	(to be filled out later)

(ii)	Sequential as possible

(iii)	Equational wherever possible
